  <name>Boxes</name>
  <summary>Virtualization made simple</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Boxes is a cross-platform virtual machine manager built with Python and Qt6.
      It supports libvirt, direct QEMU subprocess, and remote SSH backends,
      making it easy to create, manage, and access virtual machines on Linux,
      macOS, and Windows.
    </p>
  </description>
